description: L'Entrec么te Steak and Fries Bistro Pop Up offers a unique dining experience with its signature steak and fries. Located at Quayside Isle, it provides a cozy atmosphere for families and friends to enjoy a meal together. The bistro also offers a kids' menu, weekday tapas hours, and hangover brunch on Fridays to Sundays. Corkage fees apply at $35++ per bottle for wine and $55++ per bottle for spirits. Cakeage is $25++ per cake and is valid for birthdays and special occasions only. No outside food is allowed within the restaurant premises. Operating hours are Sunday to Thursday from 11:30am to 10:00pm, and Friday & Saturday from 11.30am to 11:00pm. Operating hours may vary on the eve of and on Public Holidays.
